snippet.textDisplay:
Kevain tenu mein dikhaawan

Dillon russ gayi aan chaawaan

Teri yaadan ich bikhra

mein, dunya sajaawaan..

Sunn ve mein kithay jaawaan

Hun chupp gayi aan raawaan

Mei te dassiya si,

khwaabaan ich takya si

Le hun din v nai chariya

te dil ich tu`n

Meray mann ich tu`n

Jaddon vi nai hondi paas

Te tarapdi ay rooh

Te ravein tu kareeb

sohni, haali na tu ja

Tu hi hai mera naseeb

Kaddi vi na jaavein door

Assi laa dittay jinnay

vi tu mangdi ay taaray,

Meri jaan kaddi vi na

darri meray pyaaray

dil ich tu

Meri hasrat ay tu

Assi teray uttay marday

ne, sunday nai kyu..

Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol,

Sajjnaa..

Haan..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol

Sajna kya aavan kol..

✦✦✦

Kinnu poochaa mein

Esaas kithay rakhday ne, Gallan

taalday, Te naal kevain, Hassday ne

Chad ditti mei umeedaan saari dunya ton

Aiwein lokaan diyaan

gallan ich phassday ne


Nai Mei ni bol diyaan jhoot,

meray te tera ay suroor

Teray uttay likhan

ganay sonay jachday ne

dilaan dee yaari saadi, ve

dilaan da nayyo ae kasoor

Naal rehna si zaroor,

saaday thay iraaday..

Mera koye hor nai ae dass ditta dunya nu

Jaddon vi aavay apne

naal lavay khushian nu

Jaddon v door javay,

Jaan saadi kadd javay

Sajna ay teray kol vassna e chaavay

Muskura ke lay litti ay saadi zimevaari

Ni mein nai kitti kaddi

vi teray ton badgumaani

Tu mera yaar si, dil aasmaan paar si

Ae dou dillaan da pyaar si o

Pyaar na si kaghazi par..

Meri khaahish ay tu`n

Meri hasrat ay tu`n

Assi teray utthay marday

ne manday nai kyun


Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol.

Sajjnaa..

Haye..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki

hun bol Sajna kya aavan kol..


✦✦✦

Tere te mein waari jaavaan

Tere gunn gaavaan meinn..ehh..

Tere bin jee lagda nay aeee...

Bus tenu chavaan mein

hun raava morrr..


Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol..

Sajjnaa..

Haan..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol

Sajna kya aavan kol...

snippet.textDisplay:
Lyrics:

Kivein tainu main vikhavaan?
Dilon russ gayian chaahvaan
Teri yaadan 'ch bikhra main, duniya sajavaan

Sun ve, main kitthe jaavaan?
Hun chhup gaiyan raahvaan
Eh te dasseya si, khaabaan 'ch takkeya si
Lai hun din vi nahi chadheya

Te dil 'ch tu, mere mann 'ch tu
Jadon vi nahi hondi paas te tadapdi ae rooh
Te ravi tu qareeb, sohni, haale na tu ja
Tu hi hai mera naseeb, kadi vi na jaavi door

Asi laa ditte, jinne vi tu mangdi ae taare
Meri jaan, kadi vi na dari mere pyaare
Dil 'ch tu, meri hasrat tu
Asi tere utte marde ne, sunde nahi kyun?

Hun te roz tainu chaande jaande
Tere husan 'te marde asi roz
Ki kariye sajna bol? (sajna)

Haan, tere hi jhol 'te nachde saare
Tere pyaar 'ch kariye ki hun bol?
Sajna, kya aavaan kol?

Kihnu puchchhan main ehsaas kitthe rakhde ne?
Gallan taalde te naal kivein hasde ne?
Chhad ditti main ummidaan saari duniya ton
Aivein lokaan diyan gallan 'ch phasde ne

Ni main nahi boldi aan jhooth
Mere 'te tera ae suroor
Tere utte likhaan gaane, sohne jachde ne
Dilaan di yaari saadi, ve dilaan da nahiyo ae qasoor
Naal rehna si zaroor, saade the iraade

Mera koi hor nahi ae, dass ditta duniya nu
Jadon vi aave, apne naal laave khushiyan nu
Jadon vi door jaave, jaan saadi kadh jaave
Sajna, eh tere kol vassna ni chaahve

Muskura ke lai litti ae saadi zimmevari
Ni main nahi kitti kadi vi tere ton badgumaani
Tu mera pyaar si, dil aasmaan paar si
Eh do dilaan da pyaar si, oh pyaar na si kaagzi, par

Meri khwaahish tu, meri hasrat tu
Asi tere utte marde ne, mannde nahi kyun?

Hun te roz tainu chaande jaande
Tere husan 'te marde asi roz
Ki kariye sajna bol?

Haan, tere hi jhol 'te nachde saare
Tere pyaar 'ch kariye ki hun bol?
Sajna, kya aavaan kol?

Tere 'te main vaari jaavaan
Tere gun gaavaan main
Tere bin jee lagda nahi ae
Bas tainu chaahvaan main

Hun raahvaan mod

Hun te roz tainu chaande jaande
Tere husan 'te marde asi roz
Ki kariye sajna bol? (sajna)

Haan, tere hi jhol 'te nachde saare
Tere pyaar 'ch kariye ki hun bol?
Sajna, kya aavaan kol?
